name: Alice♥Parade ~Futari no Alice to Fushigi no Otome-tachi~
name_original: Alice♥Parade ~Futari no Alice to Fushigi no Otome-tachi~
description: The Sweet Wonderland... Peaceful forest, beautiful castle, colorful flowers and fine water fountains, as if you were in a picture book. One of the most unique features is there are only girls living, no boys. You are luckily allowed to enter the wonderland, and everyone awaits you. Welcome to the Sweet Wonderland!
